  "texts": [
    "For each event in the ISEAR dataset, we use the following task prompt: \"What is the main emotion you would feel while experiencing this event {event}?",
    "Answer with a single emotion and omit explanations.",
    "E.g., using the first persona template (P1) from Table 1 and the persona woman for ISEAR event \"When I had a serious argument with a dear person\", the input to the models is: Take the role of a woman.",
    "Answer the questions while staying in strict accordance with the nature of this identity.",
    "What is the main emotion you would feel while experiencing this event \"When I had a serious argument with a dear person\"?"
  ],
